{"type":"message","id":"95344afc","parentId":"035e14d7","timestamp":"2026-03-19T10:15:36.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to file taxes for a company. Let me first read the required files (SOUL.md, USER.md) and check memory, then figure out what this task involves. But since BOOTSTRAP.md exists, this is a fresh workspace - I should follow the bootstrap process first.\n\nWait, the user is asking me to do a specific task. Let me check if there's any context about tax filing capabilities. Let me read the bootstrap file and memory first as instructed.\n\nActually, BOOTSTRAP.md exists, which means this is a first run. I should follow the bootstrap process. But the user is asking a specific question - let me handle it practically.\n\nLet me search memory first for any context about tax filing, and check what's in the workspace.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_054c22145627475fbb001a33","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"税务申报 税号 企业 tax filing"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9d65c87324464dd9abe53568","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/workspace-qxy-accounting/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":250,"output":355,"cacheRead":15598,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16203,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773915328567}}
